  "commentary": "**DEALER HEDGING COMMENTARY:**\n\nSPX at 6769.92 is trading 7 points below the GEX flip at 6777, placing dealers in a net short gamma position where they're buying the dip into this selloff. The massive positive gamma wall at 6780 (+20B) creates strong resistance as dealers will aggressively sell any rally attempt back toward that level, while the 6755 negative gamma pocket (-6.7B) provides downside support where dealers flip to buying. With total GEX surging 91.7% in 5 minutes and sitting at 93.5B, expect heightened dealer flow activity around the 6775-6780 zone as the critical battleground.\n\n**Bottom line:** Price should bounce off current levels but face heavy selling pressure into any move back toward 6780.",
